						 4 (2013), 
						<a href="https://www.pismowidok.org/en/archive/2013/4-ruin/civil-alliances-palestine-1947-1948" target="_blank">https://www.pismowidok.org/en/archive/2013/4-ruin/civil-alliances-palestine-1947-1948</a>
